high_descs: Turn to the left and right to go around the coffee table, then face it to the right.
Pick up the credit card from the middle of the table.
Carry the credit card and turn right, then right again to face the couch.
Place the credit card under the blue pillow on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Move a credit card from the table to couch.

high_descs: Go to the other side of the black table
Grab the credit card off of the table
Turn right and face the side of the sofa
Put the credit card on the sofa
anns.task_desc: Putting a credit card on a sofa

high_descs: Walk around to the other side of the coffee table.
Grab the credit card from the table.
Walk to the left edge of the sofa.
Place the card behind the nearest blue cushion.
anns.task_desc: Move a card from the table to the sofa to hide it.
